00:14:23,580 --> 00:14:25,480
-same as when you got attacked. -You could have done that too,

266
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,680
while being in this room.

267
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,480
It's a simple booby trap, all you need is some fishing line

268
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:31,580
and some hair pins to make it.

269
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:32,680
A booby trap?

270
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,780
The person who caused this commotion,

271
00:14:34,780 --> 00:14:37,280
hung the koto from the ceiling in your grandfathers' room

272
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:38,780
and then let it fall,

273
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:41,980
it was just coincidence that you got hit by it.

274
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:46,380
Minoru, you snuck in there to check out the koto.

275
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:49,380
That's right, that's how you got hit.

276
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:50,780
You don't know what you're talking about,

277
00:14:50,780 --> 00:14:52,780
