00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:41,080
it would be 'I', 'Ha' and 'I'.

397
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,480
Ihai? (Mortuary tablet)

398
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,780
You don't mean?

399
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,980
-I don't believe it... -It can't be...

400
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:58,780
-I've got it. -This is it.

401
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:00,480
Oh, thank goodness.

