00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:15,580
Now I can buy that koto back.

406
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:17,180
We owe it all to you.

407
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:20,380
Who are you anyway?

408
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:25,980
Well, the truth is, my name is Kogoro Mouri.

409
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:28,080
The... Kogoro Mouri?

410
00:21:28,080 --> 00:21:30,280
The famous private detective?

411
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,780
That's me.

412
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,880
Why didn't you tell us that earlier?

413
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:36,180
If we'd known that, we'd have asked you to look for stamps.

414
00:21:36,180 --> 00:21:39,380
And Minoru wouldn't have gotten hurt.

415
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:41,280
Yes, well...

416
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:45,480
What a selfish bunch.

417
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:13,080
Thank you for everything.

